6 AS INTRODUCED
7 An Act relating to education; creating the Federal
Education Guidance Disclosure Act; requiring the
8 State Department of Education to publish certain
documents on a website; prescribing publication
9 timeframe; construing website creation timeline;
mandating use of hyperlinks; directing retention of
10 certain rescinded documents; stating retention
requirements; defining term; providing for
11 codification; and providing an effective date.
