13
14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
16 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 24-162 of Title 70, unless there
17 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
18 A. This act shall be known and may be cited as the "Federal
19 Education Guidance Disclosure Act".
20 B. Within fifteen (15) days of receiving a guidance document
21 from the United States Department of Education, the State Department
22 of Education shall publish the guidance document on an Internet
23 website designated by the State Superintendent of Public Instruction
24
